Desc: active_warps_pm
Number of transactions for shared load accesses. Maximum transaction size in maxwell is 128 bytes
column3: any warp accessing more that 128 bytes will cause multiple transactions for a shared load instruction. This also includes extra transactions caused by shared bank conflicts.

Desc: Number of transactions for shared store accesses. Maximum transaction size in maxwell is 128 bytes
column3: any warp accessing more that 128 bytes will cause multiple transactions for a shared store instruction. This also includes extra transactions caused by shared bank conflicts.

Desc: elapsed_cycles_pm
Number of shared load bank conflict generated when the addresses for two or more shared memory load requests fall in the same memory bank.
Number of shared store bank conflict generated when the addresses for two or more shared memory store requests fall in the same memory bank.
